      <title>伯克希尔出售更多美国银行股票，自 7 月以来净赚 90 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/berkshire-sells-more-bofa-shares-netting-9-bln-since-july-2024-09-25/</link>
